Context: Changes to LLC Laptop Loan Policy effective from December 18, 2023. Interlibrary loans are provided free of charge generally, but additional charges from the lending agency may result in contact from George Brown College for discussion. Contact information: 416-415-2000, TTY: 1-877-515-5559, ask.george@georgebrown.ca. More information can be found on Library News & Services and Social Media Hub. Note: Information on this website is subject to change without notice. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
